            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> since os_delay() never drains main_loop.events, everything deferred still stalls for the whole autocompletedelay\r\n\r\nYes, that's the root cause. However, it won't be easy to improve it to asynchronous one, at least for me:(, I would do more research on it, thanks!\r\n\r\n> it's best fix in vim first.\r\n\r\nSo, for the issue witch `needs:vim-patch` label, start a PR in vim first is better?",
