            "body": "Ok, I investigate vim repo and find `inchar_loop()` that may fit your desc. So my draft is, remove delay-loop in `ins_complete`, save timestamp and set some flag instead. In `inchar_loop`, check that flag and set the `wtime` if needed, check the state in timeout branch and show the complete menu.\r\n\r\nIs there some misunderstanding? Unfamiliar with this repo. Appreciating your guidance!",
